      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST LIKE NU (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (20.18) in a Grade 4 at Q Lakeside. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Tough to beat if on-song. SWIFT RACER (8) has had a break of four months since finishing second (16.79) over 300m at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Has the ability and rates a key chance this line-up. HARDLY EASY (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 2.25 lengths from the winner (16.87). Cannot be taken lightly. GOLDEN EYE (6) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
